Source: cogutil
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: OpenCog Developers <opencog@googlegroups.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 13),
               cmake (>= 3.22),
               g++ (>= 11),
               binutils-dev,
               libiberty-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://opencog.org
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/cogpy/occ.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/cogpy/occ

Package: libcogutil
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenCog utility library (runtime)
 CogUtil is the foundational utility library for the OpenCog cognitive
 architecture. It provides essential data structures, algorithms, and
 system utilities used throughout the OpenCog framework.
 .
 This package contains the shared library for runtime use.

Package: libcogutil-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libcogutil (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenCog utility library (development files)
 CogUtil is the foundational utility library for the OpenCog cognitive
 architecture. It provides essential data structures, algorithms, and
 system utilities used throughout the OpenCog framework.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static libraries needed
 for development with CogUtil.
